             rdfs:label "mass flow controller"@en ;
             skos:definition "Device that has the function to control the flow of fluid media to a defined mass flow. It consists of a mass flow meter and a proportional valve."@en .


###  https://w3id.org/pmd/hto/HTO_0000029
